---
title: Korean-Style Beef Bulgogi Rice Bowl with Stir-Fried Veggies & Sesame Mayo
description: Fluffy rice piled with stir-fried veggies and beef bulgogi, could this be the new favourite dinner? When we season the beef with a
teriyaki sesame sauce mixture then it’s certainly a guarantee.
